      <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="zap" size={22} /></div><strong>Natural Killer Cell Activation</strong><p>Turkey tail PSK and reishi triterpenes enhance NK cell cytotoxicity — the ability to detect and destroy virus-infected and abnormal cells. NK cells are the first line of defense against viral infections and serve critical immune surveillance functions.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="leaf" size={22} /></div><strong>Adaptive Immune Enhancement</strong><p>Mushroom beta-glucans improve dendritic cell antigen presentation, helping the adaptive immune system (T-cells, B-cells) recognize and target specific pathogens more effectively. This bridges innate and adaptive immunity for comprehensive defense.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="heart" size={22} /></div><strong>Immune Modulation (Not Overstimulation)</strong><p>Unlike immune stimulants, mushroom beta-glucans modulate rather than amplify — they enhance immune intelligence and efficiency without causing the chronic inflammatory activation that can damage tissues and exhaust the immune system.</p></div>
    </div>

